attributes.review:
When I downloaded this app to check in on my favorite Cheeto puff, it actually caused my phone to glitch so badly that I passed out and woke up in an alternate dimension where Obama was president. Just when I began to feel calm for the first time in 2020, my phone glitched a SECOND TIME and I was transported back to the reality, the middle of a global pandemic that our president has completely f a i l e d to c o n t r o l. 
Although it was nice to see Obama again, the over all experience was EXCEPTIONALLY DISAPPOINTING.
Would not recommend this app :(
